library(tidyverse)
library(readxl)
library(visdat)
library(countrycode)
url1 <- "https://query.data.world/s/tw3oaknxjlqods27xzzbpa3do4rmfr"
p1f <- tempfile()
download.file(url1, p1f, mode="wb")
happy_data <- read_excel(path = p1f)
happy_data <- mutate(happy_data, happiness_score = `Life Ladder`)

happy_data$country <- as.factor(happy_data$country)

happy_data$year <- as.factor(happy_data$year)

happy_data$Generosity <- as.factor(happy_data$Generosity)

happy_data$`Social support` <- as.factor(happy_data$`Social support`)

happy_data$`Perceptions of corruption` <- as.factor(happy_data$`Perceptions of corruption`)

happy_data$`Freedom to make life choices` <- as.factor(happy_data$`Freedom to make life choices`)

happy_data$happiness_score <- as.factor(happy_data$happiness_score)


happy_data1 <- happy_data %>% select(`country`, `year`, `Generosity`,
